      <section id="teachers-part" class="pt-70 pb-120">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-5">
                <div class="section-title mt-50">
                    <h5>Featured of Pharmacy</h5>
                    <h2>Meet Our Pharmacist</h2>
                </div> <!-- section title -->
                <div class="teachers-cont">
                    <p>
                        Our pharmacist is a highly skilled and knowledgeable healthcare professional who plays a vital role in ensuring the safe and effective use of medications. With extensive training and expertise in pharmacy, our pharmacist is dedicated to providing exceptional pharmaceutical care to our patients.

                        Our pharmacist is responsible for dispensing prescription medications, providing accurate medication information, counseling patients on the proper use and potential side effects of medications, and collaborating with healthcare professionals to optimize patient care.

                        They are well-versed in various medications, their interactions, and potential adverse effects. Our pharmacist stays up to date with the latest advancements in pharmaceuticals and incorporates evidence-based practices in their work.

                        With their expertise, our pharmacist helps patients manage their medications, address concerns or questions related to drug therapy, and promotes overall wellness through medication management.

                    </p>
                    <a href="@Url.Action("VisitPharmacy","Indexview","Patient")" class="main-btn mt-55">Visit our Medicines</a>
                </div> <!-- teachers cont -->
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 offset-lg-1">
                <div class="teachers mt-20">
                    <div class="row">
                    @foreach (var item in ViewBag.ph)
                    {
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <div class="singel-teachers mt-30 text-center">
                                <div class="image">
                                    <img src="../../../../UploadImage/@item.Image" width="150" height="300" alt="teacher">
                                </div>
                                <div class="cont">
                                    <h6>@item.Name</h6>
                                    <span>Pharmacist</span>
                                </div>
                            </div> <!-- singel teachers -->
                        </div>
                    }
                    </div> <!-- row -->
                </div> <!-- teachers -->
            </div>
        </div> <!-- row -->
    </div> <!-- container -->
</section>

